                c.relname,
                CASE
                    WHEN c.relispartition THEN 'p'
                    WHEN c.relkind IN ('m', 'v') THEN 'v'
                    ELSE 't'
                END,
                obj_description(c.oid, 'pg_class')
            FROM pg_catalog.pg_class c
            LEFT JOIN pg_catalog.pg_namespace n ON n.oid = c.relnamespace
